title: Under Armour 's total workforce worldwide from 2009 to 2019
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of employees. In total the number of data points it has is 11.
In general Number of employees has rose over the Year.
Number of employees is slightly increasing from 2009 to 2011, roughly constant from 2011 to 2012, gradually increasing from 2012 to 2015, and finally roughly constant from 2015 to 2019.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2013 and 2014.
The highest Number of employees, of value 16400.0 was reached at Year 2019
The lowest Number of employees, of value 3000.0 was reported at Year 2009
